     ,"METHOD":[
	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4codes":[{"code":"EDE", "dict":"METHOD", "idict":21,"hlp":"Particle identification by `E/Delta E` measurement"}]
	,"x4freetext":[" The 3He beam was impinged on a natC target in the"
		," scattering chamber of the SE-SPS. Reaction ejectiles"
		,"were momentum-analyzed through the SE-SPS and"
		,"detected in a position- and angle- sensitive detector"
		,"system in the optical focal plane. Identification of"
		,"the desired reaction deuterons was achieved through"
		,"the correlation between the particles` energy loss (dE)"
		," through the detector gas and residual energy (E)"
		,"deposited in a plastic scintillator. The position"
		,"signals were analyzed to reconstruct the excitation"
		,"spectra of 13N* through kinematic dispersion."]
	}
